sentence.text: The correlations between the expressions of CTHRC1 with clinicopathologic features,E-integrin-mediated signaling pathway and Vimentin expression were analyzed.Result:CTHRC1 protein expression levels in papillary thyroid carcinoma tissue were significantly higher than those in adjacent normal thyroid tissue and benign disease(P<0.01);CTHRC1 expression was significantly correlated with lymph node metastases(P<0.05).

Objective:To investigate the expression and significance of cell migration in patients with papillary thyroid cancinoma.Method:We collected 63 specimens of papillary thyroid carcinoma tissue with 36 specimens of the adjacent normal thyroid tissue and 23 specimens of thyroid nodular goiter.
